reviewText:
Also, interviews and speeches by Fidel Castro in Havana during the period 1959 (the year that Castro's troops overthrew the dictator Batista and his troops to win the war. See Stephen Soderbergh's epic Che (part one).
In the years 1963 and 1964 we listened to Castro's speeches on short wave radio from our home in a Northern town in the Dominican Republic not far from La Habana, Cuba.
